"title":{
"__html":"Diagnosis"
},
"titleNode":{
"type":"section-title",
"hlId":"523223",
"children":[
"Diagnosis"
]
},
"children":[
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"ce46a2",
"children":[
"Use the 4-point Centor criteria to stratify adult patients according to risk of group A streptococcal pharyngitis:"
]
},
{
"type":"list",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"eedfcf",
"children":[
"fever (subjective)"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"479a61",
"children":[
"absence of cough"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"ba2e76",
"children":[
"tender anterior cervical lymphadenopathy"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"44ecb5",
"children":[
"tonsillar exudates"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"9d8c59",
"children":[
"Management is based on the number of Centor criteria present:"
]
},
{
"type":"list",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"216ad9",
"children":[
"≤2: neither test nor treat with antibiotics"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"6e65f2",
"children":[
"≥3: obtain a rapid antigen detection test (RADT); management is based on results"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"3a2550",
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"i",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"Fusobacterium necrophorum"
]
},
" infection should be considered in adolescents and young adults with a negative RADT and an unusually prolonged and severe pharyngitis. ",
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"i",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"F. necrophorum"
]
},
" is the causative agent of Lemierre syndrome, septic thrombophlebitis of the internal jugular vein resulting in metastatic pulmonary infections."
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"section",
"id":"mk19_bb_gm_s58_2",
"title":{
"__html":"Treatment"
},
"titleNode":{
"type":"section-title",
"hlId":"4c4ac0",
"children":[
"Treatment"
]
},
"children":[
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"1814db",
"children":[
"Select oral penicillin for 10 days. Choose a macrolide for patients allergic to penicillin. ",
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"i",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"F. necrophorum"
]
},
" is treated with ampicillin-sulbactam."
]
}
]
}
]
